title: Trustee Scholarship - Grace College
Description:: The Trustee Scholarship is available to entering students at Grace College and Theological Seminary.  You must have a minimum 3.7 GPA or rank in the top 20 percent of your class to be eligible for this award.  A minimum 1270 SAT / 27 ACT score is also required.

title: Salutatorian Scholarship - Grace College
